   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Empowering Citizens in The Bahamas</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">In the Bahamas, lack of civic participation and skepticism of governments limit the capacity for national development, sustainable growth and resilience after the dual disasters of Hurricane Dorian and the COVID-19 Pandemic. ORG will offer free  grass-roots community based sessions of civic education.  Through 1 hours Participants will learn about the Bahamas Constitution, citizens role in governance and advocacy skills.</narrative>
